### List (should be [])
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets

### Create
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Printer Broken",
  "description": "Keeps jamming",
  "createdBy": "Zulfiqar",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}

### List again (should show the new ticket, sorted by priority & time in service)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets

### Start work
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1/start

### Assign
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1/assign
Content-Type: application/json

{ "assignee": "Alice" }

### Close
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1/close

### Stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/stats

### Filters (optional)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?q=printer
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?status=OPEN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?priority=HIGH
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?assignedOnly=true
